Message: Hi, I’m the NewsBreak Ad Assistant. How can I help?

Data: {"hidden_reply": true, "form_id": "ee27568f0b9f4826a7215c8197548501", "payload": "/cancel_for_input_data"}

Message: how soon can you approve my ad?
On average, we review ads within 4 hours on weekdays, and up to 8 hours on weekends. If you have any other questions or need further assistance, feel free to ask!

We accept a variety of ad categories, but it's important to ensure that your ad content aligns with NewsBreak’s policies and guidelines. For detailed information on acceptable categories and guidelines, please refer to our Ad Policy document here: [Ad Policy](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/18085960681101-My-ad-got-rejected-What-s-next). If you have any specific category in mind, let me know!

Betting ads are generally not allowed on NewsBreak. I recommend checking out our Ad Policy document for detailed guidelines on what types of ads are permitted. You can find it here: [Ad Policy](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/25362604231053-Ad-Policy). If you have any other questions, feel free to ask!

Ads promoting weight-loss products or diets are generally not allowed on NewsBreak. For more details, please review our Ad Policy document here: [Ad Policy](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/25362604231053-Ad-Policy). If you have any other questions or need further assistance, let me know!

Yes, you can run ads promoting app installs on NewsBreak. Just make sure that your ad content complies with our policies and guidelines. For more information, you can refer to our Ad Policy document here: [Ad Policy](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/25362604231053-Ad-Policy). If you need any further assistance, feel free to ask!
